      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GATE TWO SLOY (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording six placings in a row before finishing fifth (30.44) at Richmond latest. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of five starts. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. AL'S MEMORY (6) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 5.5 lengths away in fifth (26.98). Was in the money the start prior. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Expected to feature in the finish. AURORA'S IMAGE (8) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (43.45) at Wentworth Park latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. FANTASIA SHINE (3) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
